Summary    : Open Message Passing Interface
URL        : http://www.open-mpi.org/
License    : BSD
Description: Open MPI is an open source, freely available implementation of both
           : the MPI-1 and MPI-2 standards, combining technologies and resources
           : from several other projects (FT-MPI, LA-MPI, LAM/MPI, and PACX-MPI)
           : in order to build the best MPI library available.  A completely new
           : MPI-2 compliant implementation, Open MPI offers advantages for
           : system and software vendors, application developers, and computer
           : science researchers. For more information, see
           : http://www.open-mpi.org/ .

